data.description: Welcome to this charming home located in downtown Beulaville! With its abundance of charm and character, this one-story home offers 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, providing ample space for comfortable living. As you step inside, you'll immediately notice the beautiful details that adorn this home. The main room features exquisite dental molding, adding a touch of elegance to the space. Cozy up by the stunning fireplace on chilly evenings, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. Natural light floods the interior through numerous windows, creating a bright and airy ambiance throughout.The master bedroom boasts new luxury vinyl plank (LVP) flooring, adding a modern touch to this historic gem. This room provides a tranquil retreat, perfect for unwinding after a long day. In addition to the main house, there is a finished mother-in-law shed in the backyard, providing a private and comfortable space for guests. This additional living area adds versatility to the property, making it ideal for hosting friends and family.Step outside into the charming fenced backyard, where you'll find a tire swing hanging from a majestic tree. This delightful feature is perfect for creating lasting memories with loved ones. Don't miss the opportunity to own this home, filled with charm and character and be a part of its history. Schedule a showing today and experience the timeless beauty and warmth it has to offer.
